      • execute

        public void execute()
        Creates Runnables for all available jobs, this will empty the job-Queue but without filling the TileCache at the same time! The TileCache will be filled, if the MapGeneratorJob was executed, be sure you don't add MapGeneratorJob for the same Tiles in the meantime!
